text: Teneyevskoye Rural Settlement (; , Teni jal tărăkhĕ) is an administrativeIn accordance with Law #28, the municipal divisions in the Chuvash Republic are considered to be its administrative-territorial divisions and municipal division (a rural settlement) of Alikovsky District of the Chuvash Republic, Russia.Law #37 It is located in the central part of the district. Its administrative center is the locality (a selo) of Teneyevo. Rural settlement's population: 900 (2006 est.). Teneyevskoye Rural Settlement comprises five rural localities. The Alikovo–Tautovo highway crosses the territory of the rural settlement. ==References== ===Notes=== ===Sources=== * * ==Further reading== *L. A.
